The '''Bundestag Science Prize''' (in German: Wissenschaftspreis des Deutschen Bundestages) is a science prize to the value of €10,000 that is awarded every two years for outstanding works about [[parliamentarism]]. The prize donor is the [[Bundestag|German Bundestag]].<ref>[https://www.bundestag.de/wissenschaftspreis https://www.bundestag.de/wissenschaftspreis] (German)</ref>

