The '''Ministry of Education, Research and Religious Affairs''' ({{lang-el|Υπουργείο Παιδείας, Έρευνας και Θρησκευμάτων}}) is a [[ministry (government department)|government department]] of [[Greece]]. One of the oldest ministries, established in 1833, it is responsible for running the country's [[Education in Greece|education system]] and for supervising the [[Religion in Greece|religions in Greece]]. The minister is Kostas Gabroglou. <!--The paragraph I removed was replaced by the table in the "History" section below [[User:Dimsar01]]-->
